1
00:01:30,423 --> 00:01:36,184
(Peony Berkembang)

2
00:01:36,264 --> 00:01:39,011
(Episode 28)

3
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:41,021
Kejatuhan keluarga Chen

4
00:01:41,439 --> 00:01:44,181
